<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="fn summary" style="text-align:center; font-size: 125%; font-weight: bold; text-align:center; font-size:125%;"><b>Ernst Friedrich "Fritz" Schumacher</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; padding:4pt; line-height:1.25em; text-align:center; font-size:8pt;"><a href="/wiki/File:SchumacherSiB200.jpg" class="image" title="SchumacherSiB200.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/42/SchumacherSiB200.jpg" width="225" height="308" border="0" /></a><br />
